## 
why is push gerrit HEAD:refs/for/master
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/10461214/why-is-git-push-gerrit-headrefs-for-master-used-instead-of-git-push-origin-mast

##
default to push refs/for/master instead of refs/heads/master
http://hamersun.blogspot.tw/2012/12/git-pushdefault-pushcode-review-server.html

global setting
git config remote.origin.push refs/heads/*:refs/for/*

oneshot 
git push origin HEAD:refs/for/master

